title: Qualities to Look for in a Partner while Dating
description:
Are you single and ready to mingle?! In this episode, Jeanine discusses qualities she suggests you look for in a partner while dating. Whether you're a guy or girl, hopefully this gives you something to think about during your dating process. Dating is meant for evaluation that leads to marriage, so listen as Jeanine provides many things to think about while you're dating OR single prepping for dating. Get your notepad ready cause she's got a lot of great info for your dating life! Enjoy!
